description.3: A cavalcade of clashes! First, Logan faces off with Generation X! Then, he and Jubilee face off with the mysterious cyborgs Donald Pierce and Khyber! But what do these mechanical men want with Wolverine?
description.4: A behind-the-scenes peek at the creation of the Star Wars Universe!  See how your favorite characters came to be, and get an exclusive look at the "pitch panels" from the 1998 comic series!
description.8: As a mysterious illness continues to spread across Manhattan, Wolverine and Punisher uncover its evil origins. Unfortunately, they're a little tied up fighting the battle droids that were designed to stop the Morlock called Revelation! Been wondering what could bring down the Punisher? Let's just say that this issue proves that Frank Castle isnt as invulnerable as we all thought!
description.10: Black Bolt's leadership continues to be called into question as Woz fights for survival and Black Bolt's wife Medusa fights for her very survival.
description.13: Three different governments are out to kill Black Panther! While T'Challa launches a political counter, Achebe is told by his hand puppet to terminate his alliance with T'Challa's step-mother. Madness consumes the villain.
description.14: This issue sees Steve and Sharon dealing with last issues events in their own ways. Nick Fury makes an appearance and finds himself at the mercy of Baron Blood... Can the Cap save the day?
description.15: Still with her father in his prime Spidey era, Spider-Girl finds herself against SLAYERS, SPIDERS, AND TORCHES.
description.16: As the X-Men return to Earth, what does Project: Deathlok have in store for them?
description.17: The most offbeat Hulk saga through the eyes of another! Guest-starring the Avengers!
description.20: The FF are home at last, but they don't get to enjoy it for long! Paris has been "Ruined", and the Four are the city's only hope!
description.23: With a defection from a key member and Sunspot facing governmental trouble, a limited X-Force faces down with Eternals, aliens and killer flora!
description.24: Nate fights alongside of Cyclops and Jean to defeat Hatchet-9 and return the portion of the Age of Apocalypse that has invaded the Alaskan wilderness back to his original nightmare world.
description.26: Sunset Bain recruits Stark for a Baintronics project, not foreseeing that Tony might uncover her dangerous, secret tech. The imposter War Machine attacks!
description.28: Spider-Man is trapped in an elaborate illusion of Mesmero's making! And it's driving him insane!
description.34: Will death come to Caesar by the bionic hands of CABLE?
description.35: Her world has been blockaded and her people imprisoned, but the young Queen'Amidala,recently elected to the throne of'Naboo, is a teenager of uncommon wisdom. Exiled from her home and spirited away by a pair of Jedi, Amidala will look upon every experience as a potential key to her world's problems. But her salvation may rest in the hands of another- perhaps where she least expects it!
description.36: As Ki-Adi-Mundi prepares to return to the desert wastes of Tatooine in search of a wayward Jedi, he is stopped by an old friend and mentor. The Dark woman has news for the Cerean Jedi, and he's not going to like it! Once on Tatooine, Ki meets with the crime lord Jabba the Hutt. Despite the fact that the slimy crime lord had only recently threatened the life of Ki's daughter, Ki-Adi-Mundi has no choice but to ask for Jabba's aid in his search. Ki receives the aid, but nothing from Jabba the Hutt is ever free!
description.37: The epic tale of'Kir Kanos,'Imperial Royal Guardsman, and his one-man war against'those'who seek to taint the memory of'Emperor'Palpatine through corruption and greed, has become an instant classic! No fan will want to miss this!
description.42: The hunt is on! Logan's seemingly tracked down Magneto, and he'll stop at nothing to get to him! And with his fellow X-Man Nightcrawler at his side, there's sure to be a fight waiting for them!
description.46: Continuing the team-up between the toughest men in comics! A mystery illness has struck down New York's entire Upper West Side -- and the rest of the city is next! Among the fallen lay Frank Castle's dear friend -- and she'll die unless an antidote is found! Now the Punisher and Wolverine must descend into a series of long forgotten underground tunnels to unravel the mystery of the mutant called Revelation. That is, if they can keep from killing each other!
description.48: In a dimension nestled between time itself, Cable enters the time stream to rescue Sanctity!
description.49: Flash Thompson and Spider-Man are trapped inside a "perfect world", where Flash is a hero alongside Spidey, and has helped the Fantastic Four defeat Doctor Doom! But something is wrong with this Spider-Man team-up- the Spider-Man with Flash Thompson isn't Peter Parker!
description.54: Domino enters a twisted reality of Halloween Jack, who portends that Domino's fate is sealed unless she agrees to follow him.
description.55: A piece of Nate's Age of Apocalypse reality has merged with an Alaskan mountain and he has to fight through an army of Infintes with Cyclops and Jean by his side to try and set things right.
description.57: Warbird accepts help from Stark while battling Golden-Blade and Sapper. Off the battlefield, Carol Danvers struggles with personal demons. Can Tony bring his friend back from the edge?
description.59: Triton goes to Prince Namor to plead for help on behalf of the king.
description.60: The Lord of Genosha sends a severe yet succinct warning to all those who oppose him. Quicksilver is conflicted over staying by his father's side or breaking out his own agenda. Genosha's cabinet is established, ushering in a new age of mutant supremacy.
description.63: Black Panther seeks out the men who apprehended Wakanda. But what is the evidence suggesting the American Government's involved? Who else is more suited to help than Captain America and the fearless Avengers?
description.64: Captain America's greatest love is possessed by the Red Skull!
description.65: Spider-Girl travels back in time and meets the one that started it all, The Spectacular Spider-Man!
description.66: The X-Men find themselves on a Skrull world.  But things go from bad to worse when Galactus shows up to consume the world.
description.67: The Hulk needs to catch a flight...one that's already airborne!
description.70: When you're trapped in the Negative Zone trying to escape, a battle with THIS foe is all but inevitable! Before the FF can finally return home, they must fight their way past the most unstoppable force in the Negative Zone - ANNIHILUS!
description.72: Though he has been branded a maverick, a troublesome'Jedi'with a propensity to follow his own aptitude for'the Force'in all living things,'Qui-Gon Jinn'is undoubtedly a'Jedi Knight'of the first order. But his greatest critic is his own student,'Obi-Wan Kenobi, and Qui-Gon knows that now is the time for him to prove the strength of his own convictions, for nothing less than the fate of'the galaxy'rests upon his shoulders!
description.73: Don't miss the explosive first installment of The Outlander! Ki-Adi-Mundi's first assignment after joining the Jedi Council will take him back to the fearsome deserts of Tatooine! The Jedi Council has tracked a long-wayward and powerful Jedi to the backwater world, and it's up to Ki to find him and convince him to return. Unfortunately, not only does he not want to return, but a powerful enemy has the Jedi in her sights, and a blaster bolt can travel a long way across the desert flats of Tatooine!
description.78: No matter how hard he tries, Wolverine just can't escape trouble! Between fighting genetic abominations and mad scientists, Logan has only one question: can't a guy have a drink in peace? Guest-starring Cable!
description.79: Though all eyes are on the boy'Anakin Skywalker, there is another young man making his rite of passage. The only thing standing between'Obi-Wan Kenobi'and'Jedi'Knighthood is a lesson he must learn from his'Jedi Master, but the only place where he can learn that lesson is in the middle of an intergalactic war!
description.82: It's bullet-flyin', bone-clawin' action as comics' deadliest duo unites, courtesy of Pat and Alvin Lee, the creative force behind the white-hot Darkminds! The Morlocks spoke the name Soteira in frightened whispers. She has been dead for ten years, yet her legend and legacy live on. Now, someone -- or something -- stirs beneath the concrete canyons of Manhattan, setting in motion a chain of events that draws together the feral X-Man known as Wolverine and the urban avenger called the Punisher! Logan and Frank Castle have had memorable adventures in the past -- now the stone-cold killers meet again, for the first time since the Punisher's shocking revamp! Plus: who is Revelation, and how will he or she give the world a new and deadly reason to fear mutants?
description.84: Mendicus petitions the U.N. Security Council, looking for an eleventh hour diplomatic resolution while Attilan crumbles from within.
description.85: Quicksilver has been captured by the Zealot, reduced as bait to draw out his father. Rogue and Amelia Voght make a bid for Pietro's life, leading the entire Genoshan cabinet to stage an intervention against a former mutate.
description.88: Achebe starts a riot in New York City and Black Panther can't settle this alone. Enter the Avengers! With Earth's Mightiest by his side, Panther attempts to stop a bomber before the timer drops to zero!
description.89: Captain America is sent to the 31st century and must face the evil Korvac!
description.91: The Juggernaut continues to crash from dimension to dimension...but how can the X-Men stop the unstoppable?
description.92: The Hulk is stuck in a virtual reality program! Guest-starring the Avengers!
description.95: LOCKDOWN looms over the Fantastic Four! Can Marvel's First Family pull off a Negative Zone jailbreak, and can they do it in time to save Susan from the parasitic symbiote that is slowly transforming her?
description.99: Violence erupts in the streets with a new Spider-Woman rampaging in New York City. Spider-Man, in assistance with Martha "Mattie" Franklin, tries his best to overtake the traumatized new Spider-Woman to realize she is a genetic pawn made by none other than Dr. Octopus!

0.text: Deadpool rushes to save Monty's life by taking him back to Zoe Culloden! When Zoe finally decides to help them, however, things take a turn for the worse as Deadpool, Mercedes, and Illaney are dropped off right in front of T-Ray!

2.text: The most unlikely teamup ever...it's Kang, the Supreme Intelligence and Rick Jones to save the universe!
The most unlikely teamup ever...it's Kang, the Supreme Intelligence and Rick Jone to save the universe!

3.text: A cavalcade of clashes! First, Logan faces off with Generation X! Then, he and Jubilee face off with the mysterious cyborgs Donald Pierce and Khyber! But what do these mechanical men want with Wolverine?

6.text: You’ve met the repulsive villain known as the Pig... you’ve discovered his connection to Gambit’s past... now watch as the ragin’ Cajun squares off with the ugliest, meanest fiend this side of the Big Easy! Meanwhile, one of Remy’s oldest and most bitter enemies has stumbled upon a startling secret within the X-Men, something that could swallow Gambit, and the entire team, whole!

7.text: At last, the long-awaited look at the life and times of the dearly departed Bucky Barnes! Explore the origins of Cap’s kid sidekick throughout WWII!

8.text: As a mysterious illness continues to spread across Manhattan, Wolverine and Punisher uncover its evil origins. Unfortunately, they're a little tied up fighting the battle droids that were designed to stop the Morlock called Revelation! Been wondering what could bring down the Punisher? Let's just say that this issue proves that Frank Castle isnt as invulnerable as we all thought!

9.text: Daredevil comes to Cap's aid as Loki's cruel trick on Thor is revealed.

11.text: Spider-Man vs. Bullseye. 'Nuff said! Oh, you want more info? Okay, it looks like the frightening phone calls that have plagued the Parker household reach a climax in this issue! Who is stalking the Parkers? Is it the return of Norman Osborn, or something even more insidious? And even worse, Peter takes the wrong photo of the wrong people at the wrong time. Now there¹s an underworld contract out on his life, and you won¹t believe who's behind it!

12.text: It's prom night! This time though, there will be no more surprise visitors… just kidding!

18.text: Marrow shows off her new found abilities. Rogue finds speaking her mind to be difficult.

19.text: Can Jolt defeat a foe that has squashed the entire team? The Thunderbolts and Archangel have been conquered by Graviton, who intends to have them executed as insurrectionists to his new Sky Nation! Now Jolt and Charcoal the Burning Man must grasp victory from the jaws of defeat, if they can find a way to take down a foe who controls a primal force of nature! Guest-starring X-51, the Machine Man!

21.text: Following the kidnapping of Hank Pym, the Avengers head to Wakanda where they face a most formidable foe: Alkhema, the bride of Ultron!

22.text: The Avengers defeat their evil counterparts.

25.text: It's a medical emergency for Thor's mortal host!  When an Asgardian adventure between the God of Thunder and Iron Man goes awry, a major malfunction of Mjolnir gives Thor's enemies a chance to strike him at his most vulnerable.

29.text: Spider-Man battles his greatest foe: the Green Goblin!

30.text: Spider-Man heeds the "Song of the Man-Thing!"

31.text: There's a vampire sucking the ionic energy out of his victims, and a pile of bodies is leading IRON MAN towards his doom!

32.text: The Goblin Queen instructs Bloodstorm to return her son Scotty to her. But what hidden power does Scotty possess that may be the key to stopping the Goblin Queen?

33.text: The Red Skull has revealed himself to be the source of Douglock’s current woes. With S.H.I.E.L.D. incapacitated by a techno-organic virus, will the X-Men be able to eliminate the Techno-Virus and Red Skull? A stunning, and shocking, conclusion to the Dawn of M Tech story arc!

34.text: Will death come to Caesar by the bionic hands of CABLE?

38.text: After Yelena fails to execute Black Widow, Natasha makes her way to assassinate Dr. Didier Ines, and the bio-weapon, Deathless Frenzy. With Yelena hot on her trail, Black Widow's morals are put to the test. Will she betray her mission or herself?

39.text: As Alestaire tries to get help for Deadpool via the Hell House, Deadpool makes his own grand entrance, only to be beat down by the new and unruly Hell House gang loyal to T-Ray!

41.text: The Avengers stand defeated!  What secrets about Avengers history play into the fate of the future?
The Avengers stand defeated!  What secrets about Avengers history play into the fate of the future?

42.text: The hunt is on! Logan's seemingly tracked down Magneto, and he'll stop at nothing to get to him! And with his fellow X-Man Nightcrawler at his side, there's sure to be a fight waiting for them!

44.text: Gambit’s past with the Pig revealed! The ragin’ Cajun has some unpleasant memories after discovering that the mutant trafficker Pig, has kidnapped a young boy who emits mind-controlling gas.

45.text: The Fantastic Four's Human Torch guest-stars!

46.text: Continuing the team-up between the toughest men in comics! A mystery illness has struck down New York's entire Upper West Side -- and the rest of the city is next! Among the fallen lay Frank Castle's dear friend -- and she'll die unless an antidote is found! Now the Punisher and Wolverine must descend into a series of long forgotten underground tunnels to unravel the mystery of the mutant called Revelation. That is, if they can keep from killing each other!

48.text: In a dimension nestled between time itself, Cable enters the time stream to rescue Sanctity!

50.text: Here comes Daredevil-the Man Without Fear-while the Webspinner is helpless at the hands of Kraven the Hunter.

52.text: The Avengers join forces with Thundra and her people to help overthrow the Wrecking Crew, who've taken over Arkon's realm by siphoning energy from Photon.

53.text: In their quest to find out what happened to the original Avengers, our heroes travel to a parallel reality where Dr. Doom is the supreme leader!

56.text: Asgard has been restored and the secret of Marnot shall soon be revealed! But back on Earth, Officer O'Neil makes trouble for Jake in the form of an arrest warrant!

58.text: The Red Skull's army grows and Cap has been defeated, physically and spirtually.  But there is a hope for Earth X...

61.text: Spider-Man falls into the arms of the Hunger!

62.text: An inside look at the preparations for Peter Parker's high school prom night! With the ordinary pressures and awkwardness proms exhibit, this prom should get a bit more exciting when Sandman crashes the party!

68.text: Magneto Rex ascends to power in Genosha, currying favor from the masses and gaining more following on the ground. Meanwhile, the X-team remains trapped thousands of light years away!

69.text: With Archangel flying to their side, the Thunderbolts battle Graviton! They couldn't beat him before, so what makes them think they have a chance now? Will the aid of Archangel turn the tide- or will the master of gravity pull the high flier from the sky?

71.text: The X-Men, led by Magneto, lend their might to Havok in the battle against the Goblin Queen and her army of followers.

74.text: Natasha Romanoff has been assigned to track a new bio weapon created by Dr. Didier Ines. With Yelena Belova, the soon-to-be new Black Widow, shadowing Natasha, the pair may be in for more trouble than they realize.

75.text: With Mercedes and Deadpool reunited, the Black Talon makes his move to claim the undead Mercedes as his own while a legion of zombies invades the Deadhut!

77.text: An Avenger betrays the team!  Who turns their back on their teammates with all of time and space at stake?
An Avenger betrays the team!  Who turns their back on their teammates with all of time and space at stake?

78.text: No matter how hard he tries, Wolverine just can't escape trouble! Between fighting genetic abominations and mad scientists, Logan has only one question: can't a guy have a drink in peace? Guest-starring Cable!

80.text: Rogue plays the unlikely role of 'damsel in distress’ after being kidnapped by the X-Cutioner! But why is she being used as bait to lure Gambit? Check out the fan-favorite X-couple in a team-up for the ages!

81.text: It’s a psychedelic throwback to the groovy days of Cap, S.H.I.E.L.D., and M.O.D.O.K.! Far out!

82.text: It's bullet-flyin', bone-clawin' action as comics' deadliest duo unites, courtesy of Pat and Alvin Lee, the creative force behind the white-hot Darkminds! The Morlocks spoke the name Soteira in frightened whispers. She has been dead for ten years, yet her legend and legacy live on. Now, someone -- or something -- stirs beneath the concrete canyons of Manhattan, setting in motion a chain of events that draws together the feral X-Man known as Wolverine and the urban avenger called the Punisher! Logan and Frank Castle have had memorable adventures in the past -- now the stone-cold killers meet again, for the first time since the Punisher's shocking revamp! Plus: who is Revelation, and how will he or she give the world a new and deadly reason to fear mutants?

83.text: Spider-Man is out of shape and has no sense of responsibility.  Reed Richards has doned Doctor Doom's armor.  Who can save America from the teenage Red Skull?

86.text: Kingpin's back…and he has one of his minions put Spider-Man in his crosshairs…

87.text: With the Silver Surfer now on Spider-Man's side (for now), they must band together not only to defeat Psycho-Man in the realm of Sub-Atomica, but also the powerful supervillain Annihilus!

93.text: Poetic irony? The X-Men are freed from one hellish dimension…only to arrive on the Skrull homeworld the night before it’s to be gobbled up by Galactus!

94.text: From the pages of X-Men flies the Archangel! The Thunderbolts have a new headquarters, a new transport ship and a new mission: to prove themselves by taking down the biggest villains at large! Their first target: Graviton! Their surprising ally: The X-Man known as Archangel! Now that he's no longer hangin' with the X-Men, will Warren Worthington III join the T-Bolts?

96.text: Spider-Man is transported to a medieval dimension far, far away! And he might not have a way back home!

97.text: Ben Grimm, Mole Man and Callisto run an underground escape from Goblin Queen-controlled territories until a betrayal sets The Five and their Sentinel Army on the heroes. Just when things look their darkest, a stunning arrival turns the tides!
